                  </hi>I am in the service of James Christmas, a sales<lb></lb>man, in Old-street-road—he sells all sorts of articles—on the 23rd of May, he had this pistol just by the door outside—the prisoner came by about eleven o'clock, and took the pistol, hid it, and walked away—I went in and told my master—I followed the prisoner, who had got about one hundred yards, and took him—this is the pistol—(<hi rend="italic">looking at it</hi>.)</p>
